{"tid":1900210,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"世衞（WHO): 全歐州應合力抗疫， 「封關」會打擊旅遊業","createTime":"2020-02-27T05:46:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T09:02:24.000Z","uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c2a18efc9641fd43d0bac0a210811ce187ec3ece","tid":1900210,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:46:45.000Z","msg":"新冠肺炎疫情持續擴散，歐洲多國陸續出現確診個案。截至歐洲中部時間周三（26日）晚上9時，全歐洲已有478宗確診個案，當中14人死亡。世界衞生組織（WHO）、歐盟代表及意大利政府當日在羅馬舉行特別峰會，世衞呼籲歐州各國合力抗疫，又提醒過度限制旅行會帶來負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n世衞歐洲區域負責人克盧格（Hans Kluge）表示，意大利受疫情的影響最為嚴重，最近個案數量急增，部分病人沒有明確的感染路徑，為政府帶來極大挑戰。他指意大利政府將公眾健康置於經濟繁榮之上，是艱難但正確的決定。他強調，疫情所造成的負擔最終會由各國一起承擔，因此各國無論目前是否有個案，也應合作防疫。意大利衞生部長斯佩蘭扎稱，不建議暫停履行神根公約，指各國都同意開放邊境，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">封關既無效，也不恰當</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟要求成員國評估他們應對疫情的計劃，並上報歐盟。歐盟疾控中心認為，歐洲其他國家也可能出現類似意大利的情形，但仍有信心阻止疫情進一步擴散。聯合國世界旅遊組織及世衞周三發表聯合聲明，指根據目前形勢，世衞不建議各國實施任何旅行或貿易限制。聲明提及，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">過度限制旅行會對國際交通造成不必要的干擾，對旅遊業造成負面影響</span></strong>。"},{"pid":"15f8c15480a66ce614713c82a7685c0a73283426","tid":1900210,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:47:13.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200227/mobile/bkn-20200227123010675-0227_00912_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Faeanews%2F20200227%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20200227123010675-0227_00912_001.html&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgcWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=e08f05bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/aeanews/20200227/mobile/bkn-20200227123010675-0227_00912_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"143df8a94d24b99e71b1d39452f10d7d1369aa59","tid":1900210,"uid":256246,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:47:53.000Z","msg":"世衞連旅遊業都管埋？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"155bbab984f35ba44071c63c6b90b5fb63bf97c0","tid":1900210,"uid":44562,"like":10,"dislike":2,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:48:06.000Z","msg":"WHO 講旅遊業, 我屌你個閪丫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1693d58907fc022505331ebdc70f605e7bcf0084","tid":1900210,"uid":42283,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T05:51:14.000Z","msg":"世衛差唔多係時候解散"},{"pid":"01232e38be0a49f97146214295e5fd122fa051c6","tid":1900210,"uid":46500,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:00:26.000Z","msg":"哩頭講要齊心抗疫 果頭就話封關影響旅遊業<br />\n<br />\n屌你個閪原來who將旅遊業置於人命之上"},{"pid":"5cfdc6ec0e5ff556f5e0e4a75dcd3a0dd25830b0","tid":1900210,"uid":35113,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:48:14.000Z","msg":"咁即係要抗疫定旅遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3498cab2a62069841771ed7406e61d7b6e8b3f3c","tid":1900210,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:49:45.000Z","msg":"旅遊抗疫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043daaed981b669925885e4aeb1379d864c387de","tid":1900210,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:51:19.000Z","msg":"林鄭又唔聽世衛講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898df829eac5526b407adfb0748fe9982f08c84a","tid":1900210,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:52:41.000Z","msg":"佢哋管衛生<br />\n旅遊關佢柒事"},{"pid":"e5e09f5f1bca1e090a565da2d13732cbe04cb521","tid":1900210,"uid":166308,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:54:25.000Z","msg":"WHO係唔係幫中國攬炒全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2513a30a65265f363d8846e02d4b7ad737621bda","tid":1900210,"uid":14065,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T06:54:30.000Z","msg":"世衛關心旅遊業<br />\n戇鳩"},{"pid